                  "content": "I have been teaching violin and piano for over six years, bringing both technical expertise and genuine passion to his instruction. \n\nI hold a Master's degree in Violin Performance from the Mannes School of Music, where I studied under Michelle Kim, Assistant Concertmaster of the New York Philharmonic.",
